Name: Annual
About the game: This is a classic FPS with all the 90's feel. You are a survivor of a space expedition trying to survive the alien threats at all costs. As you awake from a stasis chamber with only a blaster. Will you survive the horde or become another casualty? Features: - A sandbox world to expore. - Fast and fluid FPS gameplay. - Lots and lots and lots of enemies to kill.
